room_title: Escape room "Museum" by 60 to Escape in Chicago
room_address: Gurnee Mills, 6170 W Grand Ave. Gurnee, IL 60031
room_description: You and your group are a band of well-known thieves. You are coming out of retirement for one last heist. Turns out a local museum has acquired some jewel worth over a billion dollars. Can you steal the jewel? Or will this be the job that finally puts you behind bars?
